dc_title_s: City of Ann Arbor, Washtenaw Coty. Michigan; surveyed & published by D. A. Pettibone.
dc_description_s: Cadastral map showing buildings. Relief shown by hachures. Includes 2 ill. 1 map; 78 x 106 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
